Tirada dadka qaba cudurka Coronavirus (COVID-19) waxay si dhakhso leh u kordhin doontaa wadamada Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, laga bilaabo Janaayo 1 ilaa Maarso 15, 2020
Marka la eego dhammaan dadka qaba cudurka Coronavirus (COVID-19) waxay muujinayaan calaamado isku mid ah dalalka Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, taas oo xaqiijinaysa in, in kasta oo sababaha ay ka duwan yihiin dalalka, cudurka COVID-19 uu si dhakhso leh ugu faafi doono dhammaan dalalka.
Marka la eego horumarka Talyaaniga, wadamada, isbitaalada iyo xarumaha daryeelka degdegga ah waa in si weyn loo diyaariyaa si loo helo dadka ugu badan ee qaba COVID-19 ee u baahan daryeel, gaar ahaan daryeelka degdegga ah.
Bishii Diseembar 31, 2019, waxaa lagu qabtay dad badan oo qaba cudur neefsashada aan la garanayn oo ka dhacay magaalada Wuhan ee gobolka Hubei ee dalka Shiinaha.
Bishii Janaayo 9, 2020, Xarunta Xakamaynta iyo Xakamaynta Cudurrada ee Shiinaha ayaa sheegtay in cudurka uu ka dhashay nooc cusub oo ka mid ah coronavirus oo hadda loo yaqaan cudurka neefsashada daran ee coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Cudurka SARS-CoV-2 ayaa hadda loo yaqaan cudurka coronavirus (COVID-19).
Caddaynta hadda jirta waxay muujineysaa in 80% dadka qaba COVID-19 ay qabaan cudurro yaryar, sida xanuunka neefsashada ama neefsashada, inta badanna ay badbaadi doonaan.
14% dadka ayaa COVID-19 ka dhalanaya cudur aad u daran oo u baahan cusbitaal, 6%na waxay u baahan yihiin daryeel degdeg ah oo aad u daran.
Tirada dhimashada ee cudurka COVID-19 ee la isbitaal geliyo waa 4%.
Daraasaddan, waxaan ku falanqeyneynaa xaaladda COVID-19 ee waddan kasta oo Yurub ah/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday (UK) oo aan ku barbardhigi doonaa xaaladda gobolka Hubei ee Shiinaha.
Sidoo kale, tirada hadda jirta ee cudurrada COVID-19 ee ka dhacay wadamada Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday ayaa la barbar dhigi doonaa tirada dadka ku dhacay Talyaaniga 31 Janaayo ilaa 15 Maarso 2020.
Dadka ku dhacay COVID-19 ee Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Ingiriiska
Sida Shiinaha, COVID-19 ayaa ku faafay dalal kale, cudurka COVID-19 wuxuu ku faafay dalal kale sida uu dalkaasi u faafay.
Bishii Maarso 11, 2020, Agaasimaha Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) ayaa ku dhawaaqay COVID-19 inuu yahay cudur faafa.
5da Maarso, sheekada Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri iyo asxaabteeda ayaa ku tilmaamay dadka ugu horreeya ee Yurub ee qaba COVID-19 marka loo eego qeexitaanka WHO.
Wadamada Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub, saddexda kiis ee ugu horreeya ee cudurka ah ayaa laga soo sheegay Faransiiska 24ka Janaayo 2020; waxay ahaayeen dadka ka yimid Wuhan, Gobolka Hubei ee Shiinaha oo dib ugu soo laabtay Faransiiska.
Bishii Maarso 15, 2020, COVID-19 ayaa lagu soo bandhigay 30 dal oo ka mid ah Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday (UK), iyo tan iyo Diseembar 31, 2019 iyo taariikhdaas, 39,768 oo kiis ah iyo 1,727 qof ayaa u dhintay cudurka iyo Talyaaniga oo leh 17,750 oo cudur ah halka 1,441 ay dhinteen.
La socodsiinta tirada iyo tirada dadka la helay COVID-19
Xarunta Yurub ee La-dagaallanka iyo Ka-hortagga Cudurrada (ECDC), tirada dadka COVID-19 ee waddan kasta, oo laga helo ilo rasmi ah oo keliya sida Wasaaradaha Caafimaadka Caalamiga ah, saraakiisha caafimaadka ee caalamiga ah iyo kuwa gobolka iyo WHO, ayaa la cusbooneysiiyay maalin kasta 8h00 subaxnimo.
Macluumaadkaas ayaa loo adeegsaday si loo ogaado sida COVID-19 u faafay wadamada Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, waxaana la isbarbardhigay Talyaaniga.
Marka la eego heerarka ugu sarreeya ee COVID-19, waxaan tixgelineynaa 14 maalmood oo ugu sarreeya ee COVID-19-ka, sidaa darteed waxaan tixgelineynaa heerarka COVID-19 ee waddan kasta oo Yurub ah / Aagga Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, muddada laga bilaabo Janaayo 1 ilaa Maarso 15, 2020.
Waxaan sidoo kale soo bandhignay tirada guud ee kiisaska adduunka oo dhan 15 Maarso 2020 saacaddii 8 subaxnimo, marka la barbar dhigo tirada Talyaaniga laga bilaabo 31 Janaayo ilaa 15 Maarso 2020.
Tirada cudurrada COVID-19 ee Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday
Tirada cudurrada COVID-19 ee 14 maalmood ka dib ee ka dhacay wadamada Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday ayaa la raacayaa heerka gobolka Hubei (Shiinaha) (Tirada 1).
Wadamada Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, cudurka COVID-19 wuxuu bilaabay inuu ku soo kordho heerka ugu sarreeya qiyaastii Febraayo 21 wuxuuna ka dib u soo kordhay heerka ugu sarreeya qiyaastii Febraayo 28, 2020 (Wararka Dheeraadka ah).
Waxay si weyn u saameysay tirada dadka cudurka qaba ee Talyaaniga, laakiin heerarka cudurka COVID-19 ayaa si isku mid ah u kordhay wadamada Yurub / Aagga Dhaqaalaha Yurub (Wararka kale).
Tirada 2 waxay muujineysaa tirada guud ee dadka qaba COVID-19, ee dalalka Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday marka loo eego kuwa Talyaaniga laga bilaabo Janaayo 31 ilaa Maarso 15, 2020.
Waxay muujineysaa in, 15 March 8am, 15 dal oo kale oo ka tirsan Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday ay la mid yihiin tirada dadka cudurka qaba Talyaaniga saddex toddobaad ama ka yar ka hor.
Natiijooyinkayagu waxay muujinayaan in tirada dadka qaba COVID-19 ay si weyn u kordhin doonaan dalalka Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday.
Xogta guud ee dadka qaba COVID-19 waxay muujineysaa in cudurka faafa uu si isku mid ah u faafayo dalalka kale.
Tani waxay dhacdaa xitaa haddii dalalka ay leeyihiin ujeedooyin kala duwan, adeegyada caafimaadka ay kala duwan yihiin, iyo xitaa haddii ay jiraan kala duwanaansho kala duwan oo ku saabsan cudurka iyo xeerarka kala duwan ee loo doorto bukaanka u baahan baaritaanka COVID-19, iyo sidoo kale baaritaanka ka dib.
Bilowgii Maarso 2020, dhakhaatiirta Talyaaniga ee gobollada cudurka ayaa sheegay in 10% ka mid ah dadka qaba COVID-19 ay u baahan yihiin daryeel degdeg ah, warbaahinta ayaa sheegtay in daryeelka degdegga ah ee isbitaalada gobollada ay aad u badan yihiin.
Tirada dadka COVID-19 ee la dhigay isbitaalka iyo/ama daryeelka degdegga ah ayaa hadda ku jirta wadamada Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub oo ah 6% iyo 1% dadka (tirada aan la shaacin).
Laakiin waa in si taxadar leh loo isku daro si loo daro macluumaadka ugu dambeeya ee ku saabsan tirada dadka cudurka qaba iyo tirada dhimashada.
Daraasad lagu sameeyay 2010-11 ayaa muujisay isbeddel weyn oo ku yimid daryeelka degdegga ah iyo sariiraha dhexe ee Yurub, iyadoo 29.2 sariirood lagu sameeyay Jarmalka iyo 4.2 sariirood oo ku saabsan 100,000 oo qof oo ku nool Portugal.
Waxay muujineysaa in dalalka ay awood u leeyihiin inay ka badan yihiin ama ka yar yihiin Talyaaniga (12,5 daryeel deggan iyo sariiro dhexdhexaad ah oo loogu talagalay 100,000 oo qof sanadkii 201011).
Xallinta daryeelka bukaanka ee ka sarreysa caafimaadka, iyadoo tirada ugu dhow ee guud ahaan Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday ee ku saabsan dadka la isbitaal geliyo COVID-19 iyo 90% halista joogitaanka sariirta ee daryeelka degdegga ah, lagu daray heerka lixaad ee ECDC ee falanqaynta degdegga ah ee COVID-19.
Sababtoo ah tirada bukaanka ee ka badan meelaha kale ee Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Midowday, iyo isbitaalada xarumaha daryeelka degdegga ah ayaa badanaa loo isticmaalaa in lagu ilaaliyo dadka gobolka, macluumaadka ku saabsan cudurrada iyo sariiraha daryeelka degdegga ah waa in si xor ah loo helaa qaybta loo yaqaan Nomenclature of Level 2 Information (NUTS-2).
Xaaladaha Talyaaniga iyo kuwa hadda jira ee dalalka kale waxay muujinayaan in cudurka faafa ee COVID-19 uu si degdeg ah ugu faafayo dalalka Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Ingiriiska.
Wadamada, isbitaalada iyo xarumaha daryeelka degdegga ah waa inay diyaar u yihiin sida ay uga falcelin doonaan heerarka faafa ee SARS-CoV-2 iyo kororka tirada dadka qaba COVID-19 ee raadinaya daryeel, gaar ahaan daryeelka degdegga ah, sida laga soo xigtay deegaanada Talyaaniga ee cudurka ka jira.
Sida lagu muujiyey falanqaynta degdegga ah ee dhawaan ee ECDC, habka ugu dhakhsaha badan, ugu macquulsan uguna habboon ayaa lagama maarmaan u ah in la xakameeyo faafitaanka SARS-COV-2, in la wareejiyo dadka qaba cudurka oo la dhigo mid ka hooseeya qiimaha kontamininta; maxaa yeelay, saadaasha tirada cudurka ayaa si dhab ah u caawin doonta go'aan qaadista dadka iyo isbitaalada inay waqti u leeyihiin inay fahmaan, aqbalaan oo ay diyaar u noqdaan daryeelka haddii aan horay loo tijaabin.
Baaritaanka degdegga ah ee xaaladaha degdegga ah ayaa sidoo kale ka hadlaya nidaamyada caafimaadka ee dad badan ay ku xakameynayaan faafitaanka cudurrada faafa.
Waxaa jira fursado yar oo ay dalalku fursad u leeyihiin inay kor u qaadaan xakamaynta dadaallada ay ku sameyn doonaan si loo yareeyo faafitaanka SARS-CoV-2 iyo in cadaadis lagu saaro dhakhaatiirta.
Haddii aanay taasi dhicin, nidaamyada caafimaadka ee qaar ka mid ah waddamada Yurub / Aagga Dhaqaalaha Yurub waxay yeelan doonaan tiro badan oo dadka buka oo u baahan daryeel degdeg ah maalmaha ama toddobaadyada soo socda.
Cudurka cudurka faafa ee 2019 (COVID-19), oo ka dhashay cudurka sanbabada ee daran ee SARS-CoV-2 (SARS-CoV-2), ayaa dilay in ka badan 3,000 oo qof wuxuuna ku dhacay in ka badan 80,000 oo qof Shiinaha iyo meelo kale oo adduunka ah, taasoo ka dhigaysa mid khatar ah oo aad u weyn.
Marka la eego cudurka walaalkiis, SARS-CoV, oo sababiyay kumanaan cudurro SARS ah sanadkii 2003, SARS-CoV-2 waxay u badan tahay inay sidoo kale ka timid jiirka isla markaana ay leedahay calaamado iyo faa'iidooyin isku mid ah.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, COVID-19 waa mid aad u yar oo aan u badnayn sida SARS laakiin waa mid aad u ballaaran oo ka badan dhalinyarada oo ka badan dadka da'da ah oo ragga ah.
Maaddaama buugaagta cudurkaasi la sii kordhin doono, ujeeddada maqaalkan ayaa ah in la siiyo macluumaad ku habboon iyo in la soo bandhigo cilmi baarista ku saabsan arrintan.
Waxaa lagu falanqeeyaa macluumaadka ugu muhiimsan ee ku saabsan cudurrada faafa, aetiology, virology, sida loo ogaado, loo daaweeyo, saadaasha, iyo difaaca cudurka.
Haddii aan weli jawaab la'aan su'aalo badan, waxaan rajeyneynaa in maqaalkani uu kaa caawin doono inaad ogaato cudurkan daran oo aad ka daaweyso.
Xaflada gu'ga ee 25ka Janaayo 2020 waxay noqotay mid aan la taaban karin oo dadka Shiinaha oo dhan ay iloobi doonaan, maxaa yeelay waxaa lagu amray inay ka baxdaan xaflada oo dhan iyo toddobaadyo ka dib markii uu soo ifbaxay cudur cusub oo daran.
Fayraska ayaa si weyn u la mid ah coronavirus (CoV) oo ahaa cudurka neefta ee daran (SARS) ee 2003; waxaa loo yaqaan SARS-CoV-2 ee Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) 11kii Febraayo 2020, cudurkaas ka dhashay waxaa loo yaqaan COVID-19 (COVID-19).
Cudurka ayaa ka bilaabmay magaalada Wuhan ee dalka Shiinaha, wuxuuna si deg deg ah ugu faafay Shiinaha oo dhan iyo ku dhowaad 50 dal oo adduunka ah.
Bishii Maarso 2, 2020, fayraska ayaa sababay in in ka badan 80,000 oo qof ay ku dhacaan COVID-19, in ka badan 40,000 oo qof ayaa ka badbaaday oo laga soo daayay isbitaalka, laakiin in ka badan 3,000 ayaa dhintay.
WHO waxay ka digtay in COVID-19 uu yahay cadowga ugu weyn ee dadka iyo inuu ka daran yahay argagixisada.
Sida laga soo xigtay PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), laba bilood gudahood, haweenku waxay daabaceen in ka badan 200 oo maqaallo ah oo ku saabsan COVID-19 oo ay ku jiraan fayraska, cudurrada faafa, cilmiga nafsaaniga, sida loo ogaado, iyo daaweynta, tan iyo markii la soo saaray warbixintii ugu horreysay ee 7ka Janaayo 2020 oo ku saabsan faafitaanka fayraska.
Maqaalkani wuxuu ku soo koobayaa cilmi baarista ku saabsan arrintan si degdeg ah u faafaysa.
Haddii ay suurtagal tahay, waxaan isku dayi doonaa inaan isbarbardhigno COVID-19 SARS iyo cudurrada kale ee ka dhashay CoV, cudurka neefta ee Bariga Dhexe (MERS, oo la soo saaray 2012.)
Waxa kale oo aan ka hadli doonaa waxa aan ka baranay sida loo daaweeyo cudurka iyo saadaasha cudurka iyo su'aalo kale oo muhiim ah.
Cudurka CoVs waxaa la sheegay in uusan ahayn cudur aad u dilaa, oo ay sababaan 15% dadka qabow 4.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, heerkan, waxaan la kulannay fayrasyo laba jeer oo cudurrada COVID ah, sida SARS-CoV iyo MERS-CoV, oo ka soo jeeda cudurrada Shiinaha ee 2003 iyo Sacuudi Carabiya ee 2012, oo si dhakhso leh u faafay dalalka kale oo ay ku dhaceen cudurro iyo dhimashada tiro badan.
