Angiotensin wuxuu u magacaabaa enzyme 2 (ACE2) oo ah enzyme ka baxsan unugyada unugyada, neerfaha, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo xididdada.
ACE2 waxay joojineysaa wareejinta angiotensin-ka enzyme (ACE) iyadoo hoos u dhigeysa heerka angiotensin-II iyo kor u qaadista angiotensin-ka 1-7) si loo sameeyo daaweyn xoog leh oo lagu daaweeyo cudurada wadnaha. ACE2 waxaa sidoo kale loo isticmaalaa in lagu faafiyo coronavirus.
Enzyme-ka jidhka aadanaha waxaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Angiotensin-ka-ku-xiran enzyme 2 waa enzyme metalloenzyme ah oo ku jira Zinx oo ku yaal endothelial iyo unugyada kale.
Protein-ka ACE2 wuxuu ka kooban yahay N-terminal peptidase M2 iyo C-terminal oo ah qaadasho sanka ah oo u qaada ammonium acid.
ACE2 waxay sameysay nooc ka mid ah noocyada borotiinka ee kaliya, iyada oo ay u shaqeyneyso inay ka soo saarto enzymes-ka ka baxsan unugyada iyo maqaarka kale.
Meesha ACE2 ee unugyada ka baxsan waxay ka timaadaa transmembrane iyo enzyme kale oo loo yaqaan sheddase, ka dibna borotiinka ayaa soo baxa oo dhiigga gala ka dibna waxaa loo soo saaraa qanjirka.
ACE2 waxay ka kooban tahay xubno badan: ACE2 waxay ku xidhan tahay xajmiga unugyada sanbabada ee nooca II ee unugyada alveolarenterocytes ee unugyada yaryar, xididdada iyo xididdada endothelial iyo muruqyada fudud ee unugyada unugyada.
ACE2 mRNA waxaa ka mid ah cortex, striatum, ypothalamus, iyo brainstem.
Waxqabadka koowaad ee aCE2 wuxuu ka shaqeeyaa shaqada ACE.
ACE waxay isku xidhtaa hormoonka angiotensin I iyo angiotensin II vasoconstriction.
ACE2 waxay ku xidhan tahay carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-pPhe) oo lagu dhex xidhiidha angiotensin vasodilator (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale ku xidhan kartaa noocyo badan oo peptide ah sida [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale hagaajineysaa xakamaynta membrane ee amino acid neutral oo keena SLC6A19 oo ka soo horjeeda cudurka Hartnup.
Tijaabi borotiinka transmembrane, ACE2 waa xarunta ugu horreysa ee soo gala unugyada coronavirus, iyo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus ka yimid SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (virus ka yimid COVID-19).
Marka la fahmo, isku xirnaanta SARS-CoV2 ee SARS-CoV1 ee borotiinka S1 ee enzyme ACE2 ee unugyada sare waxay keeni doontaa endocytosis waxayna u horseedi doontaa in fayraska enzyme-ka uu ku wada shaqeeyo mid ka mid ah endosomes-yada unugyada.
Xarunta gaarka ah waxay u baahan tahay in la diyaariyo borotiinka S iyo serine protease TMPRSS2, taas oo ah daaweyn lagu ogaanayo oo waxtar leh. taas oo keentay in dadka qaarkood ay ku soo dejiyaan ACE2, unugyada, si ay u tijaabiyaan la dagaalanka caabuqa.
Hase yeeshee, ururada ardayda iyo sharciga ayaa ku doodaya in ay sii wadaan ACE-yada loo baahan yahay iyo daaweynta ARB.
Daraasad nidaamsan iyo mid meta-barasho ah oo la daabacay July 11, 2012 ayaa lagu ogaaday in daaweynta ACE ay hoos u dhigto 34% halista cudurka sanbabada.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, halista cudurka sanbabada ayaa sidoo kale hoos u dhacday dadka la daaweeyey ACE ee u badan inay si degdeg ah u qabtaan cudurka sanbabada, marka loo eego kuwa qaba cudurka wadnaha.
Daaweynta ACE waxay sidoo kale la xiriirtay yareynta cudurka sanbabada, laakiin natiijooyinka ayaa ahaa kuwo aan ka sii daranayn halista cudurka sanbabada.
Dib-u-dhaca bini-aadamka ee ACE2 (rhACE2) waa daaweyn cusub oo loogu talagalay xanuunka sanbabada, waxayna ka caawisay dhiig-baxa sanbabada iyo oksijiin-damiska ee doofaarka iyo lypopolysaccharia ee cudurka neefsashada.
Nolosha ugu yar ee rhACE2 ee aadanaha waa 10 saacadood waxayna ku shaqeyn doontaa 30 daqiiqo hal saac oo 24 saac ah.
Daraasado badan ayaa sheegaya in rhACE2 uu noqon karo daaweyn ku habboon dadka qaba diidmada neerfaha-angiotensin (RAS inhibitors) ama dadka qaba angiotensin-ka xoogga leh. rhACE2 waxaa lagu daaweeyaa caafimaad si loo daaweeyo xanuunka neefsashada.
